Global Banana Syrup Market Insights
Banana Syrup Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Banana Syrup Market Overview
The global banana syrup market has been experiencing steady growth due to the increasing demand for natural sweeteners and banana-flavored products. The market size in 2024 is valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion, with a projected compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.6% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is attributed to the rise in the health-conscious consumer base, a shift toward plant-based and organic products, and the expanding use of banana syrup in food, beverages, and cosmetic products. The market's growth trajectory is expected to continue as more consumers seek healthier alternatives to refined sugar.

